com.hazelcast.map.impl.operation

Class MapOperationProviderDelegator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.map.impl.operation.MapOperationProviderDelegator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapOperationProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WANAwareOperationProvider

    public abstract class MapOperationProviderDelegator
extends Object
implements MapOperationProvider
    Base class which basically delegates all method calls to underlying MapOperationProvider to prevent extending classes to override all methods.

    See WANAwareOperationProvider for an example.
